  <brief_title>Airtraq Versus Standard Direct Laryngoscopy in the Pediatric Airway</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparison of the Airtraq and Standard Direct Laryngoscopy in the Pediatric Airway - A Randomized Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
